  "body": "<p>Got a little misty with this month's <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/galleries/81874-sydney-main-kit-only\">Main Kit only</a> layout at <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/shop/new?aff=6cc2c70f\">Studio Calico</a>, The add-on kits sold out really quick this time, and it's really no surprise. However there are some more <a href=\"http://bit.ly/YVwsBq\">Main kits left</a>. They were so much fun to work with. Here's how this page came together. I used white mist on the arrow mask that came in the main kit, <a href=\"http://bit.ly/YVwsBq\">Neverland</a>. I do my misting outside, sometimes on the porch, sometimes in a box on the porch.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"4a-DSC_0571-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/8d2b9b2b8c3177bf.jpg?v=1782538071\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"4b-DSC_0573-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/6effe2d32ad82fa5.jpg?v=1782538073\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4c-DSC_0574-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/9269c3d71f289c57.jpg?v=1782538076\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>I changed my mind several times as to how I wanted the page oriented.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"4d-DSC_0575-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/79ac9c8d42cfb8f7.jpg?v=1782538079\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4e-DSC_0576-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/c6d0b006f8196cb4.jpg?v=1782538082\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4f-DSC_0577-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/b1bfab9ae24e02d0.jpg?v=1782538084\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4g-DSC_0578-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/b7d79e7c26135cc0.jpg?v=1782538087\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4h-DSC_0579-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/686a7ba4075013b2.jpg?v=1782538090\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4i-DSC_0580-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/5521f555407fa8e6.jpg?v=1782538092\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4j-DSC_0581-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/93fa84f6872493e6.jpg?v=1782538095\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4k-DSC_0582-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/b4e0af3f312c6c31.jpg?v=1782538098\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4l-DSC_0583-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/ac46f2d053fa1793.jpg?v=1782538101\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4m-DSC_0584-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/42bd3753847f889b.jpg?v=1782538103\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4n-DSC_0585-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/106154e891a5945f.jpg?v=1782538106\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4o-sydney-562x600.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/58baed46d9a1af72.jpg?v=1782538109\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Hope you enjoyed seeing the process! All the layouts using these amazing kits are in <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/creative-team-gallery/neverland/scrapbook/amy-tan--2?aff=6cc2c70f\">the gallery</a>. I'm also guest pinning for Studio Calico this week - you can see <a href=\"http://pinterest.com/studio_calico/amy-tan-for-sc-guest-pinner/\">the pinboard here</a>.</p>"
